Package com.salesforce.dva.argus.sdk.entity Description

Represents the set of data objects used by Argus as method parameters and results. All entities contain annotations to facilitate serialization and de-serialization to JSON using the Jackson API. In general all fields on all entities allow null values including collection and array fields.
